01:28:05.863 --> 01:28:06.823
WITH OTHER PEOPLE

01:28:06.864 --> 01:28:08.950
IS WHAT HE'S ALWAYSBEEN LOOKING FOR?

01:28:11.077 --> 01:28:12.161
AND BESIDES,

01:28:12.161 --> 01:28:15.164
