AT MY PLACE.

01:32:36.926 --> 01:32:38.427
WOW.

01:32:38.427 --> 01:32:40.096
AND THERE'S SOMEONEI'D LIKE YOU TO MEET.

01:32:40.137 --> 01:32:41.681
I WOULD LOVE THAT.

01:32:42.890 --> 01:32:45.017
MAX? YOU READY?

01:32:55.653 --> 01:32:57.280
WHAT IS THAT?

01:32:57.280 --> 01:32:59.657
APPARENTLY...

