UH, NOT... NOT ALL OF THEM.

01:33:52.918 --> 01:33:55.504
YOU ORCHESTRATEDTHIS WHOLE THING?

01:33:55.546 --> 01:33:57.006
SOME.

01:33:57.006 --> 01:33:58.507
