01:34:34.043 --> 01:34:35.419
BECAUSE I THOUGHT

01:34:35.461 --> 01:34:39.924
SHE MIGHT RESTOREYOUR BELIEF IN FATE.

01:34:39.965 --> 01:34:42.760
