01:34:58.859 --> 01:35:00.903
YOU TWO ARE SO GOODTOGETHER,

01:35:00.903 --> 01:35:01.737
AND I'M NOT ACTING.

01:35:01.779 --> 01:35:02.988
[GIGGLES]

01:35:05.324 --> 01:35:06.575
-THANK YOU.-MM.

