01:35:50.578 --> 01:35:52.204
THANKS, MAX.

01:35:52.246 --> 01:35:54.165
THANKSFOR EVERYTHING.

01:35:54.206 --> 01:35:55.499
OH, I ALMOST FORGOT...

01:35:56.792 --> 01:36:00.087
