01:36:17.146 --> 01:36:18.647
TOM?

01:36:25.446 --> 01:36:27.031
I'VE BEEN SEARCHINGFOR SOMETHING

01:36:27.072 --> 01:36:29.116
FOR A LONG TIME...

01:36:30.826 --> 01:36:33.621
AND IT'S YOU, ELLIE.

01:36:33.662 --> 01:36:34.914
I LOVE YOU.

01:36:34.955 --> 01:36:37.708
